{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"1748d","heading":"Report on wildfire, insect infestation, and disease prevention on Federal land","label":"1748d Report on wildfire, insect infestation, and disease prevention on Federal land","identifier":"/us/usc/t43/s1748d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t43/ch35/schIII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft43%2Fs1748d","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","CodificationSection was enacted as part of the Agriculture Improvement Act of 2018, and not as part of the Federal Land Policy and Management Act of 1976 which comprises this chapter.","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Definition of “Secretary”“Secretary” means the Secretary of Agriculture, see , set out as a note under , Agriculture.section 2 of Pub. L. 115–334section 9001 of Title 7"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t43/s1748d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t43/s1748d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft43%2Fs1748d%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the number of acres of Federal land treated by the Secretary or the Secretary of the Interior for wildfire, insect infestation, or disease prevention;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t43/s1748d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t43/s1748d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft43%2Fs1748d%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the number of acres of Federal land categorized as a high or extreme fire risk;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t43/s1748d/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t43/s1748d","